Package: circulaR
Type: Package
Title: Characterization of circRNAs from Total RNA-seq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Andreas", "Petri", email = "andreas.petri@gmail.com", role = "aut"), person("Kasper Thystrup", "Karstensen", email = "kathka@dcm.aau.dk", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Kasper Thystrup Karstensen <kathka@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools for detection, analysis and characterization of circRNAs from the chimeric read data of total RNA sequencing data.
    The chimeric data format that is used are based on the chimeric output "junction" format generated by the Spliced Transcripts Alignment to a Reference (STAR) alignment algorithm.
    Characterization are currently restricted to work with Ensembl-based class objects (EnsDb).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
